{"tid":1398253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟面對極權政府加黑警濫權 我哋嘅底線仲要放到幾低？","createTime":"2019-08-02T17:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T17:54:44.000Z","uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"af314032072429d178c0f46fd19b9f548ec16581","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:40:16.000Z","msg":"由612發夢發到依家 純粹想表達下<br />\n<br />\n黑警濫捕 濫權 針對年輕人已經做得咁出面<br />\n<br />\n點解黑警可以咁大膽做咁多嘢都唔驚？大家其實都心中有數啦<br />\n<br />\n首先 黑警有大大個政府支持 二哥鄧炳強用鄉黑支持<br />\n<br />\n其次 監警會 ICAC 好多高層都係由黑警坐鎮<br />\n<br />\n再者 佢哋依家係一齊犯法 就算比人查都可以夾口供 知道好大機會冇事 所以做乜都得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咁點解到呢一刻我哋仲可以容忍到？</span><br />\n<br />\n好簡單 因為好多人都怕大眾接受唔到 民意會反彈 泛民會割蓆(<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實我都好驚</span>)<br />\n<br />\n但咁樣係咪即係繼續放任黑警呢？<br />\n<br />\n我哋每次行動都損失前線 到最後前線全部比人告暴動 之後場運動就會輸 今次輸咗香港就唔會再有自由㗎喇 完完全全變成第二個新疆<br />\n<br />\n我哋其實點都比律政告暴動 點都比人屈暴徒 當護士同埋想扶起人嘅情侶 都告暴動嘅時候 我哋仲要繼續忍？<br />\n<br />\n如果真係驚到唔敢出嚟嘅話<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不如真式宣報運動失敗</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成為第二個新疆啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想做第二個新疆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我要做自由閪 不自由 毋寧死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf484ba518a211975b3c40d3565272499eaeb8f","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:41:37.000Z","msg":"點啊 各位二代新疆人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd2f143334e1bcdce2b2fa7671e478d2e558022","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:41:51.000Z","msg":"入嚟睇下啦"},{"pid":"1ad86acbe8936b789560b52da40f4aeb71e2478b","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:42:20.000Z","msg":"覺得唔啱咪屌下我囉"},{"pid":"cbc4d824041f21f8bb537e24b75fa46b0490d118","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:42:52.000Z","msg":"屌都唔敢屌？"},{"pid":"531fcb315b7cd5fa5374039739a2b88c6aacee8a","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:43:28.000Z","msg":"驚咪唔好出街囉"},{"pid":"098a14357b2b0987c6c1fda8d40d5472bec5a7c6","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"我見唔到白衣人手上有攻擊性武器嗗"},{"pid":"82c4183de7bc69ae2aa37bc3ea58fe06a1dcb849","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098a14357b2b0987c6c1fda8d40d5472bec5a7c6","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:44:39.000Z","msg":"我見唔到白衣人手上有攻擊性武器嗗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:44:51.000Z","msg":"喎"},{"pid":"e21a0ee35bb9735b9cbfaec5ae7acc579205ee2a","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"你哋連屌鳩我嘅自由都冇喇"},{"pid":"70ae489c2ce1e491ae787b1ba935a13fe3f42047","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:46:33.000Z","msg":"醒未啊？"},{"pid":"1ee5e5f557337bdc97c3c3e81772c851eff543c1","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e21a0ee35bb9735b9cbfaec5ae7acc579205ee2a","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:46:07.000Z","msg":"你哋連屌鳩我嘅自由都冇喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"醒未啊 你班撚樣"},{"pid":"a5cef203d991535796e41be2667dff01846caddf","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ee5e5f557337bdc97c3c3e81772c851eff543c1","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e21a0ee35bb9735b9cbfaec5ae7acc579205ee2a","tid":1398253,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T17:46:0